        "subject": "LU-1416 lnet: allow ksocklnd thread configurable",
        "message": "LU-1416 lnet: allow ksocklnd thread configurable\n\nReduces the number of threads to the number specified in the\nksocknal.conf file as well allows to bind those threads to specific\nprocessors:\noptions ksocklnd ncpus=12\noptions ksocklnd cpu_affinity_off=256\n\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <minh.diep@intel.com>\nChange-Id: If0df6a21de904f335e30c9c1b79770593729c0bb\n"
      },
